// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0511 — Mass File Rename (stormous)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9b78ace4-cd77-55cb-956d-4f71bb34ca72

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
